Title: Dragon Isles Supplies
Description:
<That proto-dragon must've snatched this bag of supplies off of an unlucky Dragonscale Expedition member.

Cataloger Jakes in Wingrest Embassy will know what best to do with it.>
ObjectivesText: Deliver Dragon Isles Supply Bag to Cataloger Jakes in Wingrest Embassy.
RewardText: We're always looking for more supplies, and I know just what we can do with these.
